songs.title: Frankenstein*
songs.lyrics:
Snippet

[Verse]
Mister Frankenstein
Oh, Victor Frankenstein (Ooh)
I'm Doctor Frankenstein
I'm outchea saving lives
Igor by my side (Ooh)
That's right, I made you slime (Ooh)
Tyler, create you guys, never mind (Uh)
I bet you hate that line (Woo)
That's death to everybody in my class
Columbine (Woo), pay me in decimals (Uh)
Comma signs, dollar signs
Pay me, pay me no mind
'Cause I'm outta mine, this nigga's outta mind (Uh)
Iced out pendant, Jesus
Iced out cross, missed out on church last weekend
Iced this chain, had a Dodgers pendant
Know that I'ma sin, lord forgive us (Woo)
I'ma go to church next Christmas
I remember that-that there Thanksgiving
Eatin' churches, chicken, now ain't that somethin'
[?]

[Chorus]
Ungrateful
Remember what raised you
Know about the hand that feed you
We same the same hand that gave you (Woo)
So ungrateful
None of these boys that thankful
Like what they did if they need you
